FBIS4-15446 "drsov068_v_94010" FBIS-SOV-94-068 Daily Report 7 Mar 1994 Lithuania Belarus To Permit Visa-Free Travel Until 14 Apr Belarus To Permit Visa-Free Travel Until 14 Apr WS0704162994 Tallinn BNS in English 1030 GMT 7 Mar 94 WS0704162994 Tallinn BNS English BFN [Excerpt] Vilnius, Apr 07, BNS -- The Lithuanian Foreign Ministry received a note from the Belarusian Foreign Ministry informing that Lithuanian citizens will be allowed to travel to Belarus without entry visas until April 14. Belarus introduced visa requirements for Lithuania April 3. Lithuania made the step March 1. [passage omitted]
